Title: Ep. 106 - Open Sourcing Mental Health - Part II (Julia Nguyen)
Description: We continue our conversation with developer Julia Nguyen on her mental health journey, how it's affected her life as a programmer, and what unique product decisions she has to make for "if me," her mental health open source project.
